%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': {'primaryColor': '#ffebee', 'primaryBorderColor': '#b71c1c', 'lineColor': '#37474f'}}}%%

flowchart TB
    Input[Input to Screen<br/>Customer name, aliases, DOB,<br/>nationality, address, BOs]

    Input --> NameMatch[Name Matching Engine]

    subgraph Algorithms [Matching Algorithms]
        Exact[Exact Match]
        Fuzzy[Fuzzy Match<br/>Jaro-Winkler,<br/>Levenshtein]
        Phonetic[Phonetic Match<br/>Soundex, Metaphone]
        Token[Token-Based<br/>Name token sets]
        MLMatch[ML-Based Scoring<br/>Multi-feature matching]
    end

    NameMatch --> Algorithms

    subgraph Lists [Sanctions & Watch Lists]
        OFAC[OFAC SDN + Non-SDN]
        EU[EU Consolidated List]
        UN[UN Security Council]
        HMT[HM Treasury UK]
        Other[Other national lists<br/>Canada, Australia, etc.]
        PEP[PEP Databases<br/>Refinitiv, Dow Jones]
        Adverse[Adverse Media]
    end

    Algorithms -.Compared against.-> Lists

    Algorithms --> Results{Match Results}

    Results -->|No match| Clear[CLEAR<br/>No action needed]
    Results -->|Potential match| Hit[POTENTIAL HIT<br/>Score above threshold]

    Hit --> Analyst[Sanctions Analyst<br/>Reviews hit]

    Analyst --> TrueMatch{True match?}
    TrueMatch -->|No - different person| FalsePos[FALSE POSITIVE<br/>Document and close]
    TrueMatch -->|Yes - sanctioned entity| TruePos[TRUE POSITIVE]

    TruePos --> Block[BLOCK transaction<br/>or reject customer]
    Block --> Report[Report to OFAC<br/>within 10 business days]
    Block --> Freeze[Freeze funds<br/>if applicable]
    Block --> Compliance[Notify BSA/AML Officer]

    FalsePos --> Whitelist[Add to suppression list<br/>for future screening<br/>with documentation]

    style Input fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#e65100,stroke-width:2px
    style TruePos fill:#ffcdd2,stroke:#b71c1c,stroke-width:3px
    style Block fill:#ffcdd2,stroke:#b71c1c,stroke-width:2px
    style Clear fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#1b5e20,stroke-width:2px
    style FalsePos fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f57f17
